#为了绘制气泡图，要先将非数值类型编码
def strTOnum(col):
    res = {}
    mark = 0
    for name in userinfo[col].unique():
        res[name] = mark
        mark+=1
    return res

2.1 添加：状态性特征¶

In [31]:
#求平均工资收入与非工资收入:
#将bank表按user_id分组，统计工资收入标记为1的平均交易金额即可
bank_mark1 = bank.loc[bank['工资收入标记']==1,:]
bank_mark0 = bank.loc[(bank['工资收入标记']==0)&(bank['交易类型']==0),:]

feat_avg_wage = bank_mark1.groupby(['new_user_id'])['交易金额'].agg(func=['mean'])
feat_avg_wage.reset_index(inplace=True)
feat_avg_wage.rename(columns = {'mean':'平均工资收入'},inplace=True)

feat_avg_Nwage = bank_mark0.groupby(['new_user_id'])['交易金额'].agg(func=['mean'])
feat_avg_Nwage.reset_index(inplace=True)
feat_avg_Nwage.rename(columns = {'mean':'平均非工资收入'},inplace=True)
In [32]:
#将平均工资和平均非工资收入特征连接到feature并用 (平均值or0?  发现是0比较好) 填补空缺
feature = pd.merge(feature,feat_avg_wage,on='new_user_id',how='left')
feature = pd.merge(feature,feat_avg_Nwage,on='new_user_id',how='left')
#feature['平均工资收入'].fillna(feat_avg_wage['平均工资收入'].mean(),inplace=True)
#feature['平均非工资收入'].fillna(feat_avg_Nwage['平均非工资收入'].mean(),inplace=True)
feature['平均工资收入'].fillna(0,inplace=True)
feature['平均非工资收入'].fillna(0,inplace=True)
print("特征添加成功:\n")
feature.head()

三.模型训练 & 模型评估¶

In [49]:
#线性回归——对分数进行预测
def predict_score(x_train,x_test,y_train,y_test):
    #est1:正规方程，est2:梯度下降，est3:岭回归
    est1 = LinearRegression()
    est2 = SGDRegressor(eta0=0.01,max_iter=10000,learning_rate="constant")
    est3 = Ridge()
    #训练
    est1.fit(x_train,y_train)
    est2.fit(x_train,y_train)
    est3.fit(x_train,y_train)
    y_pred1 = est1.predict(x_test)
    y_pred2 = est2.predict(x_test)
    y_pred3 = est3.predict(x_test)
    err1 = mean_squared_error(y_test,y_pred1)
    err2 = mean_squared_error(y_test,y_pred2)
    err3 = mean_squared_error(y_test,y_pred3)
    print("普通线性回归的MSE:\n",err1)
    print("梯度下降线性回归的MSE:\n",err2)
    print("岭回归的MSE:\n",err3)
#逻辑回归-对逾期进行预测并绘制AUC曲线
def predict_overdue(x_train,x_test,y_train,y_test):
    est = LogisticRegression()
    #训练
    est.fit(x_train,y_train)
    #评估
    y_p = est.predict_proba(x_test)[:, 1]
    y_predict = est.predict(x_test)
    fpr, tpr, thresholds = roc_curve(y_test, y_p)
    roc_auc = auc(fpr, tpr)
    plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], 'k--')
    plt.plot(fpr, tpr)
    plt.title(f'auc:{roc_auc :.3f}, f1 socre:{f1_score(y_test, y_predict) :.3f}')
    print('准确率:\n',est.score(x_test,y_test))
    report = classification_report(y_test,y_predict,labels=[1,0],target_names=['逾期','没逾期'])
    print("参数报告:\n",report)
